                  </hi> I am a pastry-cook, as Shoreditch—the prisoner was my apprentice. On 7th April, at night, I accidentally left my till unlocked, with about 3<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. in it whole of it, sent for a policeman, and called the prisoner in—his arms were all over soot—I asked how it came there—he said he did not know—I gave him in charge—I found the money in the soot-hole in the cellar—other people could go there.</p>
